<p></p>.<p>The uncomfortable feeling of dryness of the mouth can be annoying. <a href="https://www.medicinenet.com/dry_mouth/article.htm" rel="dt" onclick="wmdTrack('embd-lnk');">Dry mouth</a> can also lead to dental problems and infections of the mouth. Many products are now available
<a href="https://www.medicinenet.com/over-the-counter_products/article.htm" rel="pharm" onclick="wmdTrack('embd-lnk');">over-the-counter</a> as well as by prescription for the relief of chronic mouth dryness and prevention of its complications. Professional dental care is essential for optimal <a href="https://www.medicinenet.com/dental_oral_health_quiz/quiz.htm" rel="quiz" onclick="wmdTrack('embd-lnk');">oral health</a>.</p>.<p class="credits">REFERENCE:<br><br>Kasper, D.L., et al., eds. <i>Harrison's Principles of Internal Medicine, 19th Ed</i>. United States: McGraw-Hill Education, 2015.</p>